{"tid":406964,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂－ 上素生煎包","createTime":"2017-09-20T05:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-22T10:54:27.000Z","uid":30742,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d7bc875cff8f7e04063a5f9897162b90b400008f","tid":406964,"uid":30742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T05:42:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/KiERA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FKiERA.jpg&h=1f7d054a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FRtirCAh04k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFRtirCAh04k&d=%2BfIbK9R9MAKEZDb5jBH1TjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4f18a789\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FRtirCAh04k</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個係特地為我爸媽做的！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為佢地而家身在外地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，同我講過佢地果邊既中式包點好貴<br />\n唔捨得吃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n本身想我做饅頭，但我拍好後又覺得好寡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n之前係台東池上早市買過齋既生煎包，好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就想拍比佢地睇下，睇下佢地會唔會有興趣整<br />\n雖然一定唔夠台灣好食，不過希望佢地會喜歡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ！<br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁 ：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=%2BfIbK9R9MAKEZDb5jBH1TjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=b60be8db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=%2BfIbK9R9MAKEZDb5jBH1TjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=35cc12ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog:<a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=%2BfIbK9R9MAKEZDb5jBH1TjPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=c373a79a\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"21a485b5b516b62820685fe573064dcb43770fd2","tid":406964,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T05:43:07.000Z","msg":"老娘"},{"pid":"a6bc6124bbeddab9c4377cdcacbe70934558c797","tid":406964,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T05:43:48.000Z","msg":"素=辣殺"},{"pid":"094922dda3d24371eaead8a6e0d0a3a8edef0eb0","tid":406964,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T05:45:29.000Z","msg":"上素咪無汁？d肉汁先係生煎包既靈魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb4ee8dd883bbb9fae2cbcb08469235f2990033","tid":406964,"uid":30742,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T05:50:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上素咪無汁？d肉汁先係生煎包既靈魂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n炒過既菜其實本身有佢既水份係度～都濕潤的！<br />\n同埋有菜既甜味～<br />\n但你要爆汁就唔會了！～<br />\n<br />\n比老人家要岩番佢地口味！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw，我將會做肉既生煎包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3c0c308794083c0e24bc3374953d50863